    h2.
      BED onset occurs later than other eating disorders
    p.sub-head.
      The median age of onset #[nobr (21 years)] is #[span.yellow several years #[br.mobile]later] #[br.hide--mobile]than for anorexia nervosa and bulimia nervosa.#[sup 2]
